  <text>
    <body>
      <lg type="song lyrics">
        <head>A gun &amp; A Choice</head>
        <lg number="1" type="stanza">
          <l>She rots in a cage of your make </l>
          <l>Far away from your eyes</l>
          <l>You stripped all her powers to break </l>
          <l>With your love and your lies</l>
        </lg>
        <lg number="2" type="stanza">
          <l>Marooned on an island </l>
          <l>You gave her a gun and a choice</l>
          <l>But she's crazy about you</l>
          <l>She still waits around for your voice</l>
        </lg>
        <lg number="3" type="stanza">
          <l>What kind of sick, sick love is this, that you left her to die?</l>
        </lg>
        <lg number="4" type="stanza">
          <l>She rots in a cage of your make</l>
          <l>As she waits for a sign</l>
          <l>Your gun in her hand</l>
          <l>But there isn’t a choice in her mind</l>
          <l>Now there's guilt in your veins </l>
          <l>‘Cause there's guilt in your heart</l>
          <l>So there's guilt in your blood </l>
          <l>But you're oceans apart</l>
        </lg>
        <lg number="5" type="stanza">
          <l>What kind of sick, sick love is this, that you left her to die?</l>
          <l>What kind of sick, sick love is this?</l>
        </lg>
      </lg>
